```

- Replace colored inline styles with Tailwind classes:
  - Containers: `bg-gray-950 border border-gray-800 rounded`
  - Buttons: `border border-gray-700 bg-black text-white hover:bg-gray-900 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white`
  - Inputs: `bg-gray-950 text-white border border-gray-700 placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white`

### Prohibitions
- No gradients, no colored palettes, no SELECT * in CSS or HTML equivalents.
- No inline style attributes that set background/text colors other than black/white/gray.
- Do not import external themes or CSS frameworks that introduce non‑monochrome colors.

### Validation/Acceptance
- Open the home page: background is black, primary text white; no color hex other than black/white/gray in the rendered DOM.
- Health endpoint also uses the theme (if it renders HTML).
- Lint: scan project for `style=\".*(linear-gradient|#[0-9a-fA-F]{6})\"` and block unless the hex is black/white/gray; reject `background:` with gradients.

